Akon – Wakonda Senegalese/American music mogul – Akon, releases a brand new single and video tagged “Wakonda“. The song was named after the popular word ‘Wakanda‘ which a lot of people now refer to as Africa, inspired by the blockbusters ‘Black Panther’ and ‘Avengers’. ‘Wakonda‘ is also cover for Afro B‘s successful smash hit single ‘Drogba (Joanna)‘ but Akon gave it the spice we’ve all been missing. Check it out at once! DOWNLOAD AUDIO: Digital Stores The post Akon – Wakonda appeared first on Latest Naija Nigerian Music, Songs & Video – Notjustok. Source: Not just okay